{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, numerous models have combined the strengths of both CNN and Transformer, capturing both local context information and long-range dependencies to significantly enhance segmentation performance.",
    "TransFuse [37] combines the Transformer and CNN branches in parallel.",
    "It employs a self-attention mechanism and a multi-modal fusion mechanism to integrate features from different branches, and uses spatial attention to enhance local details.",
    "Former [55] employs a hierarchical Transformer encoder with a CNN decoder.",
    "Additionally, it introduces a progressive feature fusion module to integrate multi-scale features and incorporates a feature refinement module and a feature selection module for feature handling."
  ]
}